race.comment: SUN IN CUBA (6) is a last start placegetter in Grade 5 company, jumping from this box and finishing a half a length second over 350m at this track. Has a very honest record from this same draw, including a win and four minors. Should be in this for a long way. MONTY'S RETURN (1) used the inside draw to advantage last time and hit the ground running with a fast early split, but could manage only the minor money when a 1.75 lengths third at this track over 350m in 19.53. Leading chance. AGENT SUSIE (2) scored (19.39) last time out at this track and returns here after five-and-a-half months. Has never missed the frame here at the trip from three starts. Expected to feature on best form.  Something for the Multiples: JUMBUK JOHNNY (4)
